long_description: abhinav group is a well-known name in the field of infrastructure development, boasting 27 years of experience in both commercial and residential projects. since its inception, we have successfully delivered over 9 million sq. m. of built area and aim to continue this success by delivering an additional 1.5 million sq. m. every year. owning a flat is the dream of every family, and we are dedicated to making that dream a reality. the name "abhinav" signifies "the new" or "the novice," reflecting our commitment to offering something distinct to society. this is evident in our various projects, in and around pune city. the modern and unique constructional features and amenities we provide exemplify the essence of the word "abhinav". along with this, we are also redefining the luxury & green living lifestyle for people, which has clearly reflected in the positive response we receive from people across different strata of society.
